sentence: In addition to the payments described above, the Independent Chairman receives $ 50,000 annually and the Lead Independent Director, if any, receives $ 35,000, the chairpersons of the audit committee, the dividend committee and the compliance, risk management and regulatory oversight committee receive $ 7,500 and the chairperson of the nominating and governance committee receives $ 5,000 as additional retainers to the annual retainer paid to such individuals.
